#loudspeakers and amplification

## Importance of amplification:
* visceral effect
* quality of sound
* low frequency reproduction
	* subwoofer
* spatialization
* tactile experience
	* basslet
	* [YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A89dOHPqVDw)

